Contest.name: State Initiative Measure 1033
Contest.MeasureText: Initiative Measure No. 1033 concerns state, county and city revenue. | |This measure would limit growth of certain state, county and city revenue to annual inflation and population growth, not including voter-approved revenue increases. Revenue collected above the limit would reduce property tax levies. | |Should this measure be enacted into law? Yes [ ] No [ ]
